description: TrafficSteering: Table recording traffic steering events for specific cells within a given area, including timestamps, cell identifiers, and data versioning information.  dateTime: Timestamp of the event; Area_Name: Name of the geographical area; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Likely an arbitrary identifier; vsDataType: Data type indicator; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; TrafficSteering.userLabel: User-defined label (currently empty); TrafficSteering.trafficSteeringId: Unique identifier for the traffic steering event.
